backpack.name: cleric scroll of cure serious wounds

eventsquare.text: Do you wish to enter Darkmoon ?

message.value: The bushes to the south look strange. Perhaps we should investigate...

eventsquare.text:
Behind the brush you discover a hidden stairway.
Do you wish to go down the stairs ?

message.value: The wall to the west seems solid, but I feel a small draft
The carving on the east wall is some kind of magical seal.
Looks like a food storage area.
I think this is a secret passage long ago forgotten. We better be careful !

DisplayMessage.message: Prepare for something wicked this way comes !

message.value: What's that noise ? It sounds like someone humming to the south.
These catacombs look ancient and evil...
Strange... This place was built by drow, but they left this region long ago.

DisplayMessage.message: I think we have awoken some more guards.

message.value: Hold it. I think I saw something on the east wall.
I think this are the guards barracks
